<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink329">
<l>āḷvaḻak kaṟṟa pāḻpaṭu naṉantalai</l>
<l>vemmuṉai yaruñcura nīnti nammoṭu</l>
<l>maṟutaru vatuko ṟāṉē ceṟitoṭi</l>
<l>kaḻintuku nilaiya vāka</l>
<l>voḻintōḷ koṇṭave ṉuraṅkeḻu neñcē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Will my brave heart that was taken by the girl I left behind,</l>
<l>making her reach the state when dense bangles slip down [from arms], </l>
<l>defy us and cross the harsh desert in the hot enemy land </l>
<l>with ruined, wide territory, devoid of any people movement?</l>
    </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
